{"tid":1324942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"口號：啲狗對粗口已經免疫","createTime":"2019-07-16T17:01:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T01:53:43.000Z","uid":234202,"like":85,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"58c67cb4479b72978377670821480cc445cf62a8","tid":1324942,"uid":234202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:01:57.000Z","msg":"啲狗對於<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">老母被屌</span></span>已經<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">冇反應</span></span>，不如喚醒下佢地既思維，或者僅有既一點良知。<br />\n小妹就諗到以下口號，可以對前線勞苦警察表示我地既關愛之心。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">前線生死，一哥懶理，不如我地，上佢屋企</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">高層涼冷氣，前線被遺棄</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">成日咁企，辛苦你地，放低武器，市民愛你</span></span><br />\n<br />\n另，之前有巴打講過，叫黑警只會全部警察起曬鋼，建議針對「濫權」出口號，我覺得十分有道理，但自己無貨，歡迎大家學術討論。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1247122/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1247122/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c27074fe9cd00d87df78a4e43116b4ce10846ce0","tid":1324942,"uid":234202,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:03:55.000Z","msg":"集思廣益"},{"pid":"3a57eb59961b970f7b6975d91f288c0cbe488cc7","tid":1324942,"uid":266668,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:04:07.000Z","msg":"高層涼冷氣，前線被遺棄！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47955c0b07b8427bf62a3c4908a70730f730a676","tid":1324942,"uid":65738,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:04:34.000Z","msg":"佢老母接客養大佢,犬媽媽係值得尊重"},{"pid":"28e50ede16e92870ea42e62967fe742daa1d0fe1","tid":1324942,"uid":234202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:05:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7aeda2454235e54143e53ebdb4e52b882d7f97d9","tid":1324942,"uid":8014,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:06:15.